The paper discusses the challenges faced by government statistical agencies in preserving privacy while providing access to valuable data. This topic falls under the category of computer security and privacy (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the use of data analysis techniques to preserve privacy, which falls under the categories of databases (cs.DB) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the impact of privacy on society, which falls under the categories of cybernetics (cs.CY) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
